powerpc/mmu: add is_strict_kernel_rwx() helper

Add a helper to know whether STRICT_KERNEL_RWX is enabled.

This is based on rodata_enabled flag which is defined only
when CONFIG_STRICT_KERNEL_RWX is selected.

